<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN DIEGO COUNTY DIGEST: COUNTYWIDE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Glen N. Pierson has been named interim county superintendent of schools 
effective Jan. 1, replacing Tom Boysen, who has resigned to become state 
commissioner of education for Kentucky. Pierson, now assistant superintendent 
for personnel, will oversee the San Diego County Office of Education until the 
county school board names a permanent replacement for Boysen, probably next 
spring. The office provides a variety of educational services for school 
districts. 
</P>
