<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: NATIONAL TECHNICAL'S NET INCOME UP 9% FOR QUARTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
National Technical Systems Inc., a Calabasas company that provides testing and 
technical services to aerospace and nuclear power companies, said its net 
income for the third quarter ended Oct. 31 increased 9% to $257,000 from 
$236,000 a year earlier. 
</P>
<P>
The company's sales for the quarter grew 11% to $8.41 million from $7.6 million 
last year. 
</P>
<P>
For the nine months ended Oct. 31, National Technical Systems' net income 
dropped 11% to $670,000 from $749,000 in 1989. The company's sales for the 
first three quarters grew 3% from $23 million last year to $23.8 million this 
year. 
</P>
</TEXT>
