<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PR Newswire -- The sponsor of a seminar on investors relations strategies was 
incorrectly identified in a Nov. 30 story. The sponsor was PR Newswire. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
